ord'' [http://www.bach-cantatas.com/NVD/BWV988-Vartolo.htm] [http://www.jsbach.org/vartologoldbergvariations.html]\n|-\n| [[Daniel Barenboim|Barenboim, Daniel]] || October 12, 1989 || Live recording, Teatro Col\u00f3n, Buenos Aires || Erato ER2-45468 || piano<ref>Liner notes</ref>\n|-Glen Wilson 1990 Haarlem, The Netherlands, Teldec \"Das Alte Werk\" harpsichord\n| [[Bob van Asperen|Asperen, Bob van]] || July 1991 || [[Berlin]] || EMI 7 54209 DDD || ''harpsichord''\n|-\n| [[Tjako van Schie|Schie, Tjako van]] || February 1991 || Netherlands || Rondo 001 DDD || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Christiane Jaccottet|Jaccottet, Christiana]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jsbach.org/jaccottetgoldbergvariations.html|title=Goldberg Variations by Christiane Jaccottet at jsbach.org|website=www.jsbach.org|access-date=2007-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080522190324/http://www.jsbach.org/jaccottetgoldbergvariations.html|archive-date=2008-05-22|url-status=dead}}</ref> || 1991 || ||Pilz 160127 || ''harpsichord'' ''no repeats''\n|-\n| [[Virginia Black|Black, Virginia]] || 1991 ||  || Collins 70032-2 (2 CDs) || ''harpsichord,'' ''all repeats''\n|-\n| [[Maggie Cole|Cole, Maggie]] || 1991 ||  || Virgin 5 61555 (2 CDs) DDD || ''harpsichord''\n|-\n| [[Vladimir Feltsman|Feltsman, Vladimir]] || October 26, 1991 || live at the Moscow Conservatory || [http://www.musicalheritage.com/ Musical Heritage Society] 513260T DDD || ''piano''  ''All repeats''\n|-\n| [[Tatiana Nikolayeva|Nikolayeva, Tatiana]] || January 23, 1992 || Rosslyn Hill Unitarian Chapel, Hampstead, London || Hyperion Records CDA66589. Nikolayeva's 5th recording. || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Pierre Hanta\u00ef|Hanta\u00ef, Pierre]] || June 1992 ||  || Opus 111 OPS 30-84 DDD (the first of his two recordings) || ''harpsichord'' \n|-\n| [[Blandine Verlet|Verlet, Blandine]] || September 1992 || L'Eglise de Saint Hippolyte (Tarn), France || Astr\u00e9e Auvidis E 8745 (her second recording of this work). Re-released on Na\u00efve, 2012 |