ichord''\n|-\n| [[Dong-Hyek Lim|Lim, Dong-Hyek]] || 2008 || || EMI || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Sergey Schepkin|Schepkin, Sergey]] || July 22, 2008 || [[Jordan Hall, Boston]] || King International, Inc., Tokyo, Japan KKC 29 DDD; Schepkin's second recording of this work || piano\n|-\n| [[Andreas Staier|Staier, Andreas]] || 2009 || Berlin || Harmonia mundi HMU 902058 || ''harpsichord''\n|-\n| [[Sebesty\u00e9n Ny\u00edr\u0151, Ny\u00edr\u0151, Sebesty\u00e9n]] || Dec. 6, 2007, Published 2009 || Basel || MHMC Budapest || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Andrea Bacchetti|Bacchetti, Andrea]] || 2010 || Sacile (PN), Italy || Dynamic CDS-659 || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Tzvi Erez|Erez, Tzvi]] || 2010 || Toronto, Canada || Niv Classical || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Avner Arad|Arad, Avner]] || 2010 || New York City ||MSR Classics MS-1167 || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Steven Devine|Devine, Steven]] || 2010 || Suffolk, England ||Chandos 0780 || ''harpsichord''\n|-\n| [[Nicholas Angelich|Angelich, Nicholas]] || 2010 || ||Virgin Classics || ''piano''\n|-\n| [[Nick van Bloss|Bloss, Nick van]] || 2010 || Henry Wood Hall, London || [[Nimbus Records]] || piano \n|-\n|Shemer, David\n|2011\n|Christ Church, Jerusalem\n|Aria\n|harpsichord\n|-\n| [[Minsoo Sohn|Sohn, Minsoo]] || 2011 || [[Banff Centre|The Banff Centre, Alberta]] || Honens 21794 || piano \n|-\n|[[David Jalbert (pianist)|Jalbert, David]]\n|2011\n|Palais Montcalm, Qu\u00e9bec City\n|ATMA\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Alexander Gurning|Gurning, Alexander]]\n|2011\n|Flagey Studio 1, Brussels\n|Avanti\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Dan Tepfer|Tepfer, Dan]]\n|2011\n|\n|Sunnyside \n|jazz piano\n|-\n|[[Marcel Worms|Worms, Marcel]]\n|2012\n|Zeeuwse Concertzaal Middelburg, Netherlands\n|Zefir\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Maria Perrotta|Perrotta, Maria]]\n|2012\n|\n|Decca\n|piano\n|-\n| [[Kimiko Douglass-Ishizaka|Douglass-Ishizaka, Kimiko]] || 2012 || [[Teldex Studio]], Berlin || [[Open Goldberg Variations]] || piano ([[B\u00f6sendorfer]] 290 Imperial)<ref name=pd>These recordings are in the public domain, and are available via the article about the [[Goldberg Variations]].</ref>\n|-\n|Garnati Ensemble\n|2012\n|Auditorio del C.C.R. Fray Luis De Leon, Guadarrama (Madrid)\n|Sony Music 88725474372\n|arranged for string trio by Yuval Gotlibovich\n|-\n|Magalh\u00e3es, Lu\u00eds and Schumann, Nina\n|2012\n|Endler Hall, Stellenbosch University, South Africa\n|Two Pianists\n|arrangement for two pianos by Rheinberger/Reger\n|-\n| [[Robert Costin|Costin, Robert]] || Dec. 2012 || The Chapel of Pembroke College, Cambridge|| Stone Records || organ\n|-\n| [[Jeremy Denk|Denk, Jeremy]] || Jan. 2013 || Recital Hall of the Performing Arts Center, Purchase College, [[State University of New York]] || [[Nonesuch Records]] || piano ([[Steinway]]) \n|-\n|Duo Melisande\n|2013\n|Toulouse\n|Paraty\n|transcribed by Benedetto Montebello for 2 guitars, modified by the performers\n|-\n|Kawamura, Sachiko\n|2013\n|St. Bartholomew's, Brighton\n|Claudio\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Xiao-Mei, Zhu]]\n|2014\n|St. Thomas Church, [[Leipzig]]\n|Accentus\n|piano (video DVD)\n|-\n| [[Lars Vogt|Vogt, Lars]] || Mar. 2014 || Deutschlandfunk Kammermusiksaal, K\u00f6ln, Germany || Ondine ODE 1273-2 || piano \n|-\n|[[Carsten Dahl|Dahl, Carsten]]\n|2014 (recorded over 10 years)\n|K\u00e6v Studio, [[Copenhagen|Copenhagn]]\n|Tiger Music 1902350\nTiger Music 1902138\n|prepared piano\n|-\n|[[Miquel Villalba|Villalba, Miquel]]\n|2014\n|Girona Auditori, Spain\n|Aglae Musica\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Pascal Dubreuil|Dubreil, Pascal]]\n|2014\n|\u00c9glise de Notre-Dame de l'Assomption, Basse-Bodeux\n|Ram\u00e9e RAM-1404\n|''harpsichord''\n|-\n|[[Angela Hewitt|Hewitt, Angela]]\n|2015\n|Christuskirche, Firlstra\u00dfe, Berlin-Obersch\u00f6neweide\n|Hyperion\n|piano (second recording)\n|-\n|[[Alexandre Tharaud|Tharaud, Alexander]]\n|2015\n|Aix en Provence - conservatoire Darius Milhaud\n|Erato\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Lori Sims|Sims, Lori]]\n|2015\n|Dalton Center Recital Hall, Western Michigan University, Kalamazoo, MI\n|Two Pianists\n|piano\n|-\n|[[Igor Levit|Levit, 